Frame origin taken to be mid point of front axle on the body.
The inputs for the package are defined below on the topic velocitySteeringAngle
steering:
  Units: radians
  Resolution: .001
  Limits: +/- 0.687
  Configuration: +ve value is taken for left direction for a driver sitting in the car facing front.
                 -ve value is taken for right direction for a driver sitting in the car facing front.

Speed:
  Units: meters per second
  Resolution: .277
  Limits: +/- 5 (as defined in config file, absolute limit 5.5 mps)
  Configuration: +ve value is taken for forward for a driver sitting in the car facing front.
                 -ve value is taken for reverse for a driver sitting in the car facing front. 
